OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FThe "pain and hurt" of two women
OL,7,Fallegedly abused by Sir Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson is "still so visible", a
OL,9,Fcourt has heard.
OL,11,FClosing speeches have begun in the
OL,12,Fsexual offences trial of the former
OL,13,FDUP leader at Newry Crown Court.
OL,15,FProsecution barrister Rosemary Walsh
OL,16,FKC said the trial had been a "long and
OL,17,Farduous" process for the two women who
OL,18,Fallege abuse.
OL,20,FDonaldson, 63, has pleaded not guilty
OL,21,Fto 18 alleged offences.
OL,26,@nD@EOUnD@SO]pD@NOUpD@_O]xD@^OUyD@HO]
