OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FShe said it was human nature for
OL,7,Fpeople to sometimes "lock away"
OL,8,Fthoughts.
OL,10,FThe barrister said Complainant A had
OL,11,Fspent years "shelving and avoiding
OL,12,Fdealing" with alleged abuse, while
OL,13,FComplainant B "kept those memories
OL,14,Flocked away inside".
OL,16,FBut she said there had been "turning
OL,17,Fpoints" for both women which made them
OL,18,Fcome forward and report the alleged
OL,19,Fabuse to police.
