OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781700487
OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FShe said: "Issues which had been
OL,7,Fshelved and locked away surfaced,
OL,8,Fdemanding to be seen and demanding to
OL,9,Fbe dealt with."
OL,11,FTurning to the issue of why A had not
OL,12,Freported the alleged abuse before
OL,13,F2024, Ms Walsh said: "This is a woman
OL,14,Fwho has really, properly considered
OL,15,Fwhether she should put her head above
OL,16,Fthe parapet.
OL,18,F"She knew this would not just be a
OL,19,Fnormal case. It was a huge, huge
OL,20,Fdecision to make and not one she made
OL,21,Flightly."
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@OO]uD@VOUzD@AOU}D@IO]
