OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FShe said Complainant B had "blamed
OL,7,Fherself" for the alleged abuse.
OL,9,FMs Walsh said both women had gone to
OL,10,Fpolice in 2024.
OL,12,FShe said: "Yes, two voices are better
OL,13,Fthan one... this process is difficult."
OL,15,FShe said it had been a "long and
OL,16,Farduous process" which had culminated
OL,17,Fin several hours of questioning in
OL,18,Fcourt.
OL,20,FThe barrister said: "Their pain and
OL,21,Fhurt is still so visible."
