OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FShe added: "This is not something they
OL,7,Fare doing for the fun of it."
OL,9,FMs Walsh said: "Today, you see two
OL,10,Fwomen at a time when they are ready
OL,11,Ffor this... they have not always been
OL,12,Fthat way."
OL,14,FThe barrister said neither woman has a
OL,15,F"full or complete recollection" of the
OL,16,Falleged abuse, stating some memories
OL,17,Fare "fragmentary".
OL,19,FBut she told the jury that is the way
OL,20,Fmemory of childhood events can work.
