OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FShe said both alleged victims remember
OL,7,F"distinctive incidents".
OL,9,FThe barrister referred to a meeting
OL,10,FComplainant B had with Donaldson while
OL,11,Fstaying at a Christian centre in Armoy
OL,12,Fin Co Antrim in the 1990s.
OL,14,FMs Walsh said it was clear
OL,15,F"reconciliation at that stage was the
OL,16,Fpurpose of the meeting".
OL,18,FShe said: "No-one asked this girl
OL,19,Fexactly what the abuse was she had
OL,20,Freferred to.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@WO]wD@AOUxD@WO]zD@KOU
