OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FShe said: "It underlines this is not
OL,7,Fsomething that has been fabricated on
OL,8,Fa whim."
OL,10,FMs Walsh told the jury they had
OL,11,Fwatched police interviews with both of
OL,12,Fthe alleged victims.
OL,14,FShe said: "You are the people that
OL,15,Fhave to assess if you are sure that
OL,16,Fthey are telling the truth."
