OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FReferring to an incident where
OL,7,FComplainant B alleges she was raped by
OL,8,FDonaldson, Ms Walsh said: "She recalls
OL,9,Fthe breathing, laboured and panting
OL,10,Fand the hope he would stop and lose
OL,11,Finterest."
OL,13,FRecounting an alleged incident where B
OL,14,Fclaimed Donaldson lifted her top, she
OL,15,Fsaid: "In the dark, he treats her like
OL,16,Fthe object she is to him."
