OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FReturning to the meeting at the Co
OL,7,FAntrim Christian Centre between
OL,8,FComplainant B and Donaldson in the
OL,9,F1990s, Ms Walsh said it was "clear
OL,10,Fthere was very little discussion and
OL,11,Fvery little conversation".
OL,13,FShe said: "This meeting had the
OL,14,Fpotential to be explosive because
OL,15,Feveryone, including Mr Donaldson, knew
OL,16,Fit concerned a serious allegation."
OL,18,FShe added: "We say Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,19,Fshut that meeting down, he knew this
OL,20,Fwas a problem that needed to be dealt
OL,21,Fwith, he took control of that meeting."
OL,26,@qD@]OUsD@YO]uD@KOUxD@cO]zD@LOU}D@gO]
