OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FShe said Donaldson "knew what the
OL,7,Fmeeting was about and stopped
OL,8,Fquestions".
OL,10,FMs Walsh said: "He was there to manage
OL,11,Fa problem and he did that very well
OL,12,Findeed."
OL,14,FThe barrister said Donaldson had shown
OL,15,Ffrom his account of the meeting he was
OL,16,F"willing to lie".
