OL,3,C'Pain and hurt' of Donaldson's alleged
OL,4,Cvictims 'still so visible', court told
OL,6,FMs Walsh said it was a matter for the
OL,7,Fjury to decide whether the letter
OL,8,F"refers to the hurt" of A.
OL,10,FShe added that the prosecution say the
OL,11,Freference to "deep wounds" in the
OL,12,Fletter is "highly significant".
OL,14,FThe case continues.
